## Installation
```shell script
$ pip install django-version
```

## Usage
1. Append `django_version` to `INSTALLED_APPS`
1. Append `django_version.VersionMiddleware` to `MIDDLEWARE`
1. Set your project version into the setting key `PROJECT_VERSION` as a string
